            "stanza_text": "Il reste la mélancolie\nQuand le bonheur s’en est allé.\nAlors il faut bien qu’on oublie\nOu qu’on ne soit pu consolé,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Mais, comme l’oubli serait pire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Sans le vouloir on se souvient,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et la lèvre essaye un sourire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Qu’on effort cruel y retient.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais, comme l’oubli serait pire,\nSans le vouloir on se souvient,\nEt la lèvre essaye un sourire\nQu’on effort cruel y retient."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Souvenir, oubli, même chose,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Faite de douceur et de fiel !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "— Porte d’amour ouverte et close,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Azur et tristesse du ciel !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Souvenir, oubli, même chose,\nFaite de douceur et de fiel !\n— Porte d’amour ouverte et close,\nAzur et tristesse du ciel !"
